    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed every single weekend, and it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you look with a magnifying glass, you might find a tiny speck of character, but to me, she\u2019s absolutely perfect. I\u2019m looking for a good home for her where she\u2019ll be just as appreciated. Swing by for a coffee and a look; I promise you\u2019ll fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E92 M3, strictly maintained for the discerning enthusiast. This S65 naturally aspirated V8 has been meticulously sorted with preventative rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The DCT transmission logic has been flashed for lightning-fast engagement, and the chassis remains taut with zero subframe fatigue. Finished in a flawless Alpine White with a ceramic-sealed clear coat, this specimen exhibits zero parasitic draw or fluid weeping. A turn-key masterpiece for those who demand mechanical perfection.",
