      "description": "Step into a living legacy. This isn't merely a vehicle; it\u2019s a masterwork of automotive poetry, preserved with a devotion that borders on the sacred. The luster of its finish catches the light like a polished jewel, while the interior welcomes you with the rich, unmistakable scent of heritage and luxury. Every turn of the key is a symphony\u2014a smooth, soulful resonance that speaks of a life lived in the fast lane of elegance. It handles the asphalt with the poise of a dancer, offering a ride so seamless it feels like gliding through time itself. This is a rare chance to own a pristine chapter of history, a machine that doesn't just drive\u2014it inspires.",
      "price": 43900.0,
